    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit dynamics. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings, maintaining the chassis's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and steering feedback. While the car shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is robust, the compression is strong across all cylinders, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator.",
